metadata.name: Funkies #1
metadata.description: A 10k collection of 3D Avatars with a twist! With customizable goggles these Juice drinking fast driving fashionable freaks from the depths of the tinfoil tunnels are latest creation from the mad scientist… The Funkies origins: Have you ever sat back and wondered what would happen if you cross a yeti dna with an ape? Well thankfully you don’t have to wonder anymore! Our mad scientist has taken this and turned it into reality! That’s right folks a freak experiment has gone wildly right and the funk your smelling is the smell of success!
